    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2008-07-31</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2008-08-06T18:29:25Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Calls for the enactment of laws that: (1) make more American energy available for exploration and production, including in the Arctic National Wildlife Refuge, the Offshore Continental Shelf, and federal lands onshore, including for shale oil and coal-to-liquid production; and (2) streamline the permitting process for building American refineries and allow the construction of refineries on federal lands.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
